  <div class="icons">
    <img src="../public/ikoner.png" alt="Ikoner" />
    <a href="/" class="btn">READ MORE</a>
  </div>

  <div class="text">
    <h2>SUSTAINABILITY</h2>
    <p>At TÓKI House, sustainability is a fundamental part of who we are and how we operate.</p>
